      "id": "brushfit-guide",
      "name": "BrushFit: The 2-Minute Toothbrush Workout Guide",
      "description": "22 illustrated bodyweight exercises you do while brushing your teeth. 31-page PDF with 4-week progressive program.",
      "price": {
        "amount": "19.99",
